 data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFUPbmIocoB2sqeDEvQQbP9qZco4%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU3VIZYPGVVFNVNJ4IMZF4THNEM.jpg&h=b4bf6473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■不少市民到街站寫信支持被拘控的47名民主派。"}]}